<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42001b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42001b">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42001b"> 1(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> errors of Rome</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Declaration: a letter from 49 ladies to the bishop of Montreal]</font> Sir, &mdash; Since God has, in His infinite mercy, been pleased to show us the <mark>errors of Rome</mark>, and has given us strength to abandon them to follow Christ, we deem it our duty to say a word on the abominations of the confessional. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) xii</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
